<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">Welcome back to The Best &amp; =
The Brightest. I=E2=80=99m <strong>Leigh Ann Caldwell</strong>.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">It was another chaotic day in D=
=2EC., full of mean tweets, <a href=3D"h=
ttps://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF=
9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVdFRTV0dUcEFiQ2FuVnFLenZmRT0iLCJocmVmIjoia=
