ay1qci13aXRoLWhpcy1hbnRpLXZheC1vbmVzaWVzLWluLXN1cnJlYWwtc2VuYXRlLXNjZW5lLz9=
1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249VGhlK0Jlc3QrJTI2K1RoZStCcmlnaHRlc3QrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMj=
gxJTJGMjklMkYyNSUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9jb250ZW50PVRoZStCZXN0KyUyNitUaGUrQnJpZ2h0Z=
XN0Ky0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MSUyRjI5JTJGMjUlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWls=
X2FjdGlvblx1MDAyNnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9Y3VzdG9tZXIuaW9cdTAwMjZ1dG1fdGVybT1mNmM2MDY=
xN2RhNDJhYmQxMmEiLCJpbnRlcm5hbCI6ImY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSIsImxpbmtfaWQiOj=
IwNjQ3Mzd9/ec69436799b79fd356e436b24ecab2acda60ab43b6948aa7530f04d2d385021b=
" style=3D"text-decoration: underline; color: #d40000;">weird onesies</a>, =
and confusing directives from the White House. I=E2=80=99ll have more on th=
e latter below the fold. Here=E2=80=99s hoping, at least, that House Republ=
icans got tan and hit par while golfing down in Miami during their annual r=
etreat in Doral, because based on all the intel I=E2=80=99m gathering, it=
=E2=80=99s going to be a tough slog when they get back to the icy streets o=
f Washington.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">Plus, it=E2=80=99s the eve of <=
strong>Tulsi Gabbard</strong>=E2=80=99s confirmation hearing to be Director=
 of National Intelligence. Of all <strong>Trump</strong>=E2=80=99s nominees=
, she=E2=80=99s the one most in peril. Senators tell me she needs to hit it=
 out of the park with members of the Intelligence Committee=E2=80=94somethi=
ng she hasn=E2=80=99t been able to do in some of her private meetings with =
them.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0px;">=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 0;"><em>But first=E2=80=A6</em></p>
