ight-alt: 25.5px;">
<tbody><tr>
<td style=3D"padding-bottom:8px;">
<div style=3D"margin-left:-20px">
<ul style=3D"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; list-style-type: revert;">
<li style=3D"Margin: 0 0 24px 0;"><em>Kennedy, considered</em>:<em> </em>Ea=
rlier today, noted anti-vaxxer and Trump=E2=80=99s pick to run the Departme=
nt of Health and Human Services, <strong>Robert F. Kennedy Jr.</strong>, fa=
ced the first of two Senate committees considering his vexed nomination. De=
mocrats asked tough questions, pressing Kennedy about his views on vaccines=
, antidepressants, and abortion. But the reality, obviously, is that only R=
epublicans have the power to confirm or kill his nomination=E2=80=94and the=
re wasn=E2=80=99t a whole lot of dissent. In today=E2=80=99s hearing before=
 the Senate Finance Committee, in fact, the <em>only</em> Republican signal=
ing skepticism was Senator <strong>Bill Cassidy</strong>=E2=80=94a doctor w=
ho is also the chairman of the Health, Education, Labor, and Pensions Commi=
